name: We'll Never Meet But Know That I Love You.
description: ‘We'll Never Meet But Know That I Love You’ is a collaborative animation and soundscape project between myself Omgidrawedit and alt pop musician and producer SVVIM. We journey into the places we imagine to exist beyond our reach in galaxies we will sadly never visit. Asking the question, who and what is out there. A collection of 5 worlds will be created and released over the next year. (copyright)@omgidrawedit. For personal use only. Find us on Instagram and Twitter @omgidrawedit @letsvvim
